sqlQuery.name: SQL2
sqlQuery.sqlText: select obj_code, obj_desc, obj_org, obj_mrc, obj_value, obj_commiss, dbo.repgetdesc('EN','CLAS', obj_class, 'OBJ', null) class from r5objects where obj_code = #prompt('EQUIP')#

sqlQuery.name: SQL1
sqlQuery.sqlText:
select distinct obj_code, year(odp_enddate) "Year", odp_bookvalue "Book Value", case when year(odp_enddate) <= year(getdate()) then (select sum(dbo.REPLABOUR(EVT_CODE)) + sum(dbo.REPMATERIAL(EVT_CODE)) from r5events where evt_object = obj_code and evt_object_org = obj_org and year(evt_target) = year(odp_enddate)) else dbo.GET_COMPOUND_VALUE(thisyear, #prompt('MAINT_INC')#, year(odp_enddate) - year(getdate()) ) end "Maint Cost"
from r5objects inner join r5objdepreciation on obj_code = odp_object and obj_org = odp_object_org inner join (select evt_object tequip, evt_object_org torg, sum(dbo.REPLABOUR(EVT_CODE)) + sum(dbo.REPMATERIAL(EVT_CODE)) thisyear from r5events WHERE year(evt_target) = year(getdate()) group by evt_object, evt_object_org) t on tequip = obj_code and torg = obj_org
where datepart(month,odp_enddate) = 12 and odp_mode = 'M' and obj_code = #prompt('EQUIP')# and obj_org = #prompt('ORG')#

sqlQuery.name: SQL3
sqlQuery.sqlText: select evt_code "Work Order", evt_desc "Description", evt_target "Date", dbo.repgetdesc('EN','UCOD',evt_jobtype, 'JBTP',null) "Work Type", dbo.repgetdesc('EN','UCOD',evt_status, 'EVST',null) "Status", dbo.replabour(evt_code) "Labor Cost", dbo.repmaterial(evt_code) "Material Cost" from r5events where evt_type in ('JOB','PPM') and evt_object = #prompt('EQUIP')# and evt_object_org = #prompt('ORG')#
